node.text: #NationalAviationDay happy national aviation day I’m giving away this $1000.00 active noise reduction headset to one lucky winner.  How you enter is just by tagging a friend in my video below or tag a pilot that deserves a brand new headset.  I’ll pick a winner this coming Monday. #aviationinfluencer #pilot #pilolife #anrheadset #cirruslife #Aviationheadset#giveaway #aviationday #TheShah
